          maximizing profitability for businesses across diverse industries
        </p>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-300 mt-10 md:mt-12 pt-8">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[360px_1fr] gap-8 lg:gap-10 items-start">
            <img
              src="/images/about.webp"
              alt="Team meeting"
              class="w-full rounded-2xl object-cover aspect-[4/3]"
            />
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-base">
              Our team of experienced consultants is dedicated to delivering
              exceptional results by understanding your challenges and goals,
              crafting customized strategies, and implementing effective
              solutions that propel your business forward
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
